-= Livingroom =-
Well, here we are in a livingroom. You begin to take stock of what's in the room.

You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice a sofa. The sofa is comfy. The sofa appears to be empty.

There is an open fiberglass door leading north. There is an exit to the south.
